ues with naming conventions. Just gotta keep everything organized!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_06ae88b401d58188016a0b8a1423a0819c80f0c4bd4dcf6fbd\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqC4oiqw7UCry3R1QNhX4CPA7P-5hAn5ErFsh1NxcP2mdWxa1LeSBcJo4aCBNwoGTtHFfb_aLu1E5joNt2mQSn9LGBrDq3bduxo2ElmwvjMY9tWPen9I-DMYKD3QCmppSFq-eRXp5LqV_1fzmxrKCObsBCGIZOJ5y2P7AMtHPm6YUFBSmAHJnKYu0_zqpteYkkO4t5rG1kprGqM92KSX0Etz2AdkluHKHOXVhoNXNip4k-oC2B32D9dX8ETI0V2sm_J_GEa9nJXa68QQ_rRY1jRInNpE83oJMuk8AKshXS8n4FgrMo9Rc0rkkl7a2bL-7Q_MnxPBx_jfDxd5-InwEw7UuVREcvqUeI3E6e2VgKIMoiwgA-eDHt7V1djfkrpqefn3ATgU269HN91ivv8Uq5mjZgBfVl8E0ww4ePORIKvm_wBSEkxM4LGHjgJjCXKk2uaAckhLVhXU-QUcfgFHEL0S_yKZgjZaC_ctFGr9-3QARgsE-JwTHRQdjw0wDoOlQtr9_8IvSdO5we0t0-hSDxVdy3QGGUk_TIymmedEhpQTYjbHLOcseFS6HRAqwDhRh6zSx_Vx0f4zAWDXHfDaycPFriA-cYsvsdce7TWp2ElK711ZXt-y627U32XGRfX98fHxSIL70IcknS1Iebb_j4OP6d2AzBBTuS-_FtrHfWDey0DAnpcujgsuk3_fsYzgdzje-FbVfvljGHJm1pStD9Cu3Gp-aNIcvVLyOY7ZKwfdzbO_lGm4G9-mj6deO8FiXSm_erAiWl6zSS74TTrFkfg6BRVAfHxJ8S3isNxXYAKsrejL7BJ3dCIgxdS7LNEdhECd9ve18Wl5suPl8WlaL-4pJv_QZrdKD-fMslUdqe_9iq77HfekL8IvHy4C2-F5IGTIMxEGLasuw9zyi3uSVYZZU-4injcfAf9ZJBwSobh6OQmUS5_6RPXKaktPRwYbwrY80TwPqB7Aeoy-mlLC5AviP5Apw2qihWFE3Lo9v9_C7REK9n_wRBnLwdrwXkENspXaIkChpygkj14GuxE5A4IxmPeVfCc6S9MNSacjD6cMeYp4NnJaBLg_MADlYYIpU62xmBjiC81Smo9PBLBgcmAV4OrH7ie3KlzwLd7ehdsZBs12ij_Byfcx2Jqmgk33NsiUEQCNbdgBj6aBUVjDylTbu_dMDY-k8Vqm1PNFgVTjJsrSgoOZX0ErmL1cowgM_XYoR5DpnOTaJRdoZOUddkxYAZQWoa3-5e3zrB89_HVn1ngDBTh7sH3RmFwc4uj9028TLRoX9DxYhmikSrNhHx0W7BgTRoykG2nTVzBs8DB70T1otl73smFgpehBGQTLVA6xyimvhrL3w4F0AxAfsvHasCsP7L37F0IZL6TCCEXLSAJzeBugFu1riQo7quAeYvV0afQ-DlxeYk40jVwDBVEfiPudV5IZjr499gtQuREEXSAjouv8Pk3JaOtcIfBEph0HLUwh07jv2L3fDkvY4XZ2QczccK68HKMp3tfwbyzdDmCNoqna-bgrY6q4q5YQYc2Q2opWKjyCqa_8sT0_38XvtlhiFhNdoWe3YtatKu2nQ5hCqjpITr2iUtRaFxVkk3VtBjbJHt9Z7v-95WdcPLFt4HfnkQCVe-e88YF4Z2O-Le5lYVG-GZYhXqrIJAAM3EX45ADcgYS3-1iwTQwx6UQGGtbx_NBIPLIky5sJN1W83YJ61WPp6KqncqEJ-69xfWcszrpshr3GYhuH8iYDRfEMyEa8s8MS-bDd9JirwNF9s2GHaeP1BpI2-QshyK